---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<BaseLayout title="Tim Chen | New Site" description="全新开始的个人站点。" canonical="/">
  <main id="content" class="shell">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-card">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">fresh start</p>
          <h1>Tim Chen</h1>
          <p class="lead">
            网站内容已清零，保留了离线 Markdown 备份。接下来从零开始设计和发布新内容。
          </p>
          <div class="actions">
            <a class="pill" href="/about/">关于</a>
            <a class="pill" href="https://github.com/chenyuqing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">GitHub</a>
          </div>
          <p class="section-desc" style="margin-top: 1.25rem;">
            下一步可以直接开始新栏目、新文章和新设计系统。
          </p>
        </div>
        <aside class="panel-list">
          <div class="panel">
            <span>内容状态</span>
            <strong>线上内容已清零</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="panel">
            <span>备份状态</span>
            <strong>117 篇旧文已导出为 Markdown</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="panel">
            <span>技术栈</span>
            <strong>Astro 静态站 + GitHub Pages</strong>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
